# Auth Flows — Tradly Boilerplate

## Architecture

```
Component
  → useSignInMutation / useSignUpMutation / etc.   (state/auth/api.ts)
      → authAPI.signIn / signUp / etc.             (api/auth.ts)
          → TradlySDK.user.*                       (Tradly JS SDK)
      → dispatch(setCredentials(user))             (state/auth/slice.ts)
          → state.auth.* updated + cookies written
```

**State updated automatically — never manually:**
- `signIn`, `verifyOtp`, `socialSignIn` → `dispatch(setCredentials(user))` → all auth fields populated + cookies set
- `signUp`, `resendOtp` → `dispatch(setVerifyId(verify_id))` → `state.auth.verifyId` set
- `refreshAuth` → `dispatch(updateTokens(...))` → `authKey`, `refreshKey`, `tokenSetAt` refreshed
- `logout` → `Object.assign(state, initialState)` + cookies cleared + **cart cache reset** + **listing cache reset**

**SDK payload builder:** `buildSdkPayload` (wraps in `data`, sends `pkKey`) — only for `TradlySDK.user.*`

