## What NOT to do

```ts
// Never pass uuid from a component — added automatically in api/auth.ts
signIn({ email, password, uuid: deviceId, type: 'customer' })

// Never set auth state manually
dispatch(setCredentials(user))  // only authApi does this

// Never write cookies from a component
document.cookie = 'auth_key=...'

// Never navigate inside a queryFn — component decides
```
